    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean by \"let it go\"? it's not like i can just click a button and the debt disappears. it feels like i'm stuck in this loop forever. like no matter what i do, i'm just digging a deeper hole. how am i supposed to just let go of something that's literally destroying my life?",
